metadata.name: Paradise Sound Pack
metadata.description:
Introducing the "Paradise Sound Pack" by Ramzoid â€“ 115 innovative and experimental sounds carefully crafted to level up your music. This pack is a fresh spin on classic trap drums, with Ramzoid's distinct style audible throughout.

Ramzoid gravitates towards darker sounding music, so naturally the pack is infused with haunting elements and distorted sounds that work well with these vibes. However, the pack is versatile and full of unique textures layered into the samples, making it an essential tool to stand out from the crowd for both seasoned and aspiring music producers of any genre.
